# Visa2026.Blazor.Server

- **Role:** XAF Blazor application host, `Model.xafml` (copied to output), Web API / Swagger as already wired.
- **Avoid:** moving domain or persistence rules here when the rest of the codebase keeps them in **Visa2026.Module**. Host-only changes (middleware, `Program.cs`, Blazor-specific registration) belong here.
